==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stylish
<hw>Styl"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having style or
artistic quality; given to, or fond of, the display of style; highly
fashionable; modish; <as>as, a <ex>stylish</ex> dress, house,
manner</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Styl"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
-- <wf>Styl"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

